               <head>Akbarnāmah by Abu ʼl-Faz̤l, dafter 2</head>
               <msContents
                  class="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh85064913 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh2008115921 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/sh2008115920 http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n80002413">
                  <summary>Part of the second daftar of Abu ‘l-Fazl’s Akbarnāmah covering the years
                     1580-1605, arranged in two parts: regnal years 25-36 (ff. 1-129) and 37-50 (ff.
                     130-208). </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_608C-item1">
                     <author key="viaf_5150639">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Abū al-Faz̤l ibn Mubārak, 1551-1602 </persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">ابو الفضل ابن مبارك علامی</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20880">Akbarnāmah </title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">اکبر نامه</title>
                     <colophon>The 2nd dafter of the <title>Akbarnāmah</title> was completed in the
                        reign of Muḥyī al-Dīn Muḥammad Awrangzīb in the month Day, regnal year 38
                        [ie 39] corresponding to 13 Jumada I 1107 (20 Dec 1695). The word 2nd has
                        been crossed out and glossed underneath in yellow as daftar 3. </colophon>
                     <note>
                        <p>part 1: (<locus>ff. 1v-129r</locus>) regnal years 25-36. </p>
                        <p>part 2: (<locus>ff. 130v-208v</locus>) regnal years 37-50. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
